The Vorticon guild are descendants of the vampire families of the East Tirun
continent. We are the warriors of the night, highly skilled in all manners
second to none. We are always in pursuit of our ascension for when we will take
our rightful place amongst our blood brethren. The Vorticon are not bothered by
the politics of the world for we know in the end the righteous and malevolent
alike, shall be serving us...

